## Limitations

The research is limited by the availability of online sources and the potential for incomplete historical records. Some sources may not provide comprehensive coverage of the topic, and there may be a lack of firsthand accounts from the individuals who served. Additionally, the focus on African American women may overlook the broader contributions of other minority groups during the war.